Invocation Name: introduce me
des:
Ask Alexa to tell you all about who Sian is, what she's done, & where she's going. 

To start, just say "Alexa, Introduce me" or "Alexa, open Introduce me" to hear the intro.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
